'''羅賓·蕾哈娜·芬蒂'''，{{postnom|list={{link-en|國家英雄勳章|Order of National Heroes|NH}}}}（{{lang-en|Robyn Rihanna Fenty}}，{{IPAc-en|r|i|ˈ|æ|n|ə}}<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.businessinsider.com/hard-to-pronounce-celebrity-names-2012-5?op=1|title = Hard-To-Pronounce Celebrity Names|date = 2012-05-18|work = Business Insider|accessdate = 2014-10-26|archive-date = 2016-03-04|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304060609/http://www.businessinsider.com/hard-to-pronounce-celebrity-names-2012-5?op=1|dead-url = no}}</ref>，{{bd|1988年|2月20日|catIdx=Rihanna}}），是一名[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]的歌手、詞曲作家、演員、商人、時尚設計師及外交官。她出生于[[聖邁克爾區_(巴巴多斯)|聖邁克爾區]]，并在[[布里奇敦|布里奇敦]]长大。2003年，蕾哈娜在唱片制作人[[卡尔·斯特肯与埃文·罗杰斯|埃文·罗杰斯]]的指导下录制了一些样本唱片，初涉乐坛。最终，她与[[Def_Jam唱片|Def Jam唱片]]行政總裁[[Jay_Z|Jay Z]]签下合同，正式开启个人职业生涯。在发行錄音室專輯《[[太陽之歌_(專輯)|太陽之歌]]》與《[[娜妹天下|娜妹天下]]》時，蕾哈娜創造了《[[百聽不厭|百聽不厭]]》與《[[求救訊號_(歌曲)|求救訊號]]》等熱門歌曲，並因此小有名氣。2007年，蕾哈娜發行了她的第3張錄音室專輯《[[娜妹好坏|娜妹好坏]]》，重塑了自己的音樂風格和公眾形象。專輯的首張單曲《[[小雨傘|小雨傘]]》成為了她個人職業生涯全球化的一大突破，不僅取得了較大的商業成功，還獲得了[[第50届格莱美奖|第50届格莱美奖]]最佳饒舌/演唱對唱獎。這之後，蕾哈娜又發行了四張錄音室專輯，並創造了數首熱門單曲。

至今，蕾哈娜的全球唱片銷量已超過3億，是[[畅销音乐艺人列表|唱片銷量最多的艺人之一]]。在《[[加把劲_(蕾哈娜歌曲)|加把劲]]》發行之後，蕾哈娜已正式超越[[麥可·傑克森|麥可·傑克森]]，成為《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》史上擁有第4多冠軍單曲的藝人。<ref name="billboard1">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts-decade-end?#/charts-decade-end/digital-songs-artists?year=2009|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100715151758/http://www.billboard.com/charts-decade-end#/charts-decade-end/digital-songs-artists?year=2009|archivedate=2010-07-15|title=Digital Songs Artist of the Decade|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2010-07-29|deadurl=yes}}</ref><ref name="billboard2">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/charts-decade-end/artists-of-the-decade?year=2009&begin=11&order=position|title=Artists Of The Decade Music Chart|work=Billboard|accessdate=2011-07-11|archive-date=2011-10-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/62OtgJtp1?url=http://www.billboard.com/#/charts-decade-end/artists-of-the-decade?year=2009&begin=11&order=position|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Hot1002010s">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5557804/hot-100-55th-anniversary-top-100-songs-word-cloud-top-artists|title=Hot 100 55th Anniversary: Top 100 Songs Word Cloud, Top Artists Map & More|work=Billboard|accessdate=2013-08-04|archive-date=2016-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219045506/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5557804/hot-100-55th-anniversary-top-100-songs-word-cloud-top-artists|dead-url=no}}</ref>蕾哈娜在其職業生涯已獲得多項獎項，包括8個[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]、12個[[全美音樂獎|全美音樂獎]]、12個[[公告牌音乐奖|《告示牌》音樂獎]]和2個[[全英音樂獎|全英音樂獎]]。而由於她時尚造型多變，她亦在2014年收穫了[[美國時尚設計協會|美國時尚設計協會]]終身時尚成就獎。2012年，《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》將蕾哈娜列為該年第4有權勢的名人，《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代]]》也將其評為該年百大影響力人物之一<ref>{{cite web|title=The World's 100 Most Influential People: 2012|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2111975_2111976_2111948,00.html|website=Content.time.com|accessdate=2016-09-09|archive-date=2016-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161224213822/http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2111975_2111976_2111948,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年12月，蕾哈娜入選彭博資訊公布的2019年「[[彭博|彭博]]50」名單<ref>{{Cite web | url =https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2019-bloomberg-50/#rihanna | title =RIHANNA | publisher =Bloomberg | language =en | accessdate =2019-12-09 | archive-date =2019-12-08 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20191208050451/https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2019-bloomberg-50/#rihanna | dead-url =no }}</ref>。
2021年11月，蕾哈娜榮獲“巴貝多國家英雄”稱號，使她有權使用“{{link-en|The Right Excellent|The Right Excellent}}”尊稱。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/barbados-declares-diamond-rihanna-national-hero-2021-11-30/| title = Barbados declares 'diamond' Rihanna a national hero| publisher = Reuters| date = 2021-11-30}}</ref>

==早年生活==
[[File:Bridgetown2.jpg|thumb]]长大。]]

羅賓·蕾哈娜·芬蒂出生于1988年2月20日<ref name="scribd2">{{cite web|title=''Fenty v. Arcadia Group Records''|url=http://www.scribd.com/doc/143299252/Fenty-v-Arcadia-Group-Brands|accessdate=2013-05-23|page=4|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054311/http://www.scribd.com/doc/143299252/Fenty-v-Arcadia-Group-Brands|dead-url=no}}<!-- Yes, Scribd isn't a reliable source per [[WP:USERGENERATED|WP:USERGENERATED]], but this document was uploaded by a reporter at Buzzfeed, which can be trusted for the purposes of a citation like this; see http://www.buzzfeed.com/alexrees/rihanna-not-actually-suing-topshop-for-5-million --></ref>的巴巴多斯[[聖邁克爾區_(巴巴多斯)|聖邁克爾區]]。她的母亲莫妮卡是一名非裔圭亞那退休会计，父亲羅納德·芬蒂是一名具有爱尔兰血统的非裔巴巴多斯仓库主管。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Spivey|first=Lisa|title=Rihanna, The New Cover Girl|newspaper=[[Los_Angeles_Sentinel|Los Angeles Sentinel]]|volume=72|issue=23|date=January 2007|page=B.5|issn=0890-4340}}</ref><ref name="People">{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/rihanna/biography|title=Rihanna: Biography — Part 1 & 2|work=[[人物_(雜誌)|People]]|accessdate=2008-12-16|archive-date=2008-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081217063124/http://www.people.com/people/rihanna/biography|dead-url=no}}</ref>蕾哈娜有两个兄弟，两个同父异母的姐妹和一个同父异母的兄弟。<ref name="ew">{{cite news|last=Watson|first=Margeaux|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20043393,00.html|title=Caribbean Queen: Rihanna|work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2007-06-22|accessdate=2008-11-27|archive-date=2014-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021171420/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20043393,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Clark|first=Noelene|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/gossip/2011/04/rihanna-half-siblings-family-sisters-brother.html|title=Rihanna's secret family: two half-sisters, a half-brother — and two nieces|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2011-04-18|accessdate=2011-07-21|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915210635/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/gossip/2011/04/rihanna-half-siblings-family-sisters-brother.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>小时候，蕾哈娜住在[[布里奇敦|布里奇敦]]的一个三层高的小平房中。然而，当时，她的父亲一直酗酒且对吸食[[可卡因|可卡因]]成瘾。因此蕾哈娜父母的关系很快紧张了起来。而蕾哈娜的健康状况也一直不佳，因为头痛，她被迫做了许多[[CT扫描|CT扫描]]，蕾哈娜回忆这段经历说：“医生们甚至认为那是肿瘤，因为头痛太剧烈了。”<ref name="ew"/>蕾哈娜的亲生父母在她14岁之前离婚了，而蕾哈娜的健康状况有所好转。<ref name="People"/><ref name="Biography Today">{{cite journal|year=2008|title=Rihanna 1988–|journal=Biography Today|volume=17|issue=2|page=90|publisher=Omnigraphics|issn=1058-2347}}</ref>自幼，蕾哈娜就听了许多[[雷鬼|雷鬼]]音乐，在约7岁时，她开始试着唱歌。<ref name="ew"/><ref>{{cite web|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1652415/rihanna-louds-man-down-gangsta.jhtml|title=Rihanna Says Loud's 'Man Down' Is 'Gangsta'|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]. [[維亞康姆|Viacom]]|date=2010-11-16|accessdate=2011-07-27|archive-date=2011-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806073208/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1652415/rihanna-louds-man-down-gangsta.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>蕾哈娜先后在查理斯·F·布鲁姆纪念小学和（{{lang|en|Charles F. Broome Memorial Primary School}}）康伯米尔学校（{{lang|en|Combermere School}}）就读。<ref name="ew"/>但后来她决心辍学追随自己的音乐梦想。<ref>{{cite news|last=DePaulo|first=Lisa|url=http://www.gq.com/women/photos/201001/rihanna-video-photos?currentPage=2|title=Good Girl Gone Badass|work=[[GQ|GQ]]|date=January 2010|accessdate=2011-07-27|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111093226/http://www.gq.com/women/photos/201001/rihanna-video-photos?currentPage=2|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==职业生涯==

===2003年–2004年：生涯开端===
2003年，蕾哈娜与她的两名同学组成了一个三人音乐组合。<ref name="ew"/>而偶然的一次机会，她们在巴巴多斯被美国唱片制作人[[卡尔·斯特肯与埃文·罗杰斯|埃文·罗杰斯]]发掘。几人参加了罗杰斯举行的面试。<ref name="ew"/>在面试时，蕾哈娜表演了[[天命真女|天命真女]]的歌曲《[[Emotion_(Samantha_Sang歌曲)|Emotion]]》和[[瑪麗亞·凱莉|瑪麗亞·凱莉]]的歌曲《[[英雄_(瑪麗亞·凱莉歌曲)|英雄]]》。<ref name="TheGuardian1">{{cite news|last=Patterson|first=Sylvia|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2007/aug/26/popandrock|title=Singing in the rain|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|publisher=Guardian News and Media|date=2007-08-27|accessdate=2011-09-24|location=London|archive-date=2012-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120208170722/http://www.guardian.co.uk/music/2007/aug/26/popandrock|dead-url=no}}</ref>罗杰斯后来评论说：“蕾哈娜走进房间之后，仿佛其他两个女生都不存在了。”<ref name="ew"/> 由于被蕾哈娜的表现打动，罗杰斯决定与她的母亲会面，并在不久后邀请蕾哈娜去美国录制一些[[樣本唱片|樣本唱片]]以送往唱片公司。<ref name="TheGuardian1"/>2004年，由于蕾哈娜只在假期有空参与录制，因此，蕾哈娜录制了两首样本歌曲，包括《百聽不厭》和《{{lang|en|The Last Time}}》，最终收录于她的出道录音室专辑《[[太阳之歌_(专辑)|太阳之歌]]》中<ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|url=http://www.boomsbeat.com/articles/153/20140127/50-interesting-facts-about-rihanna.htm|title=50 Interesting Facts About Rihanna|work=|publisher=Booms Beat|date=2014-01-27|accessdate=2016-02-20|archive-date=2016-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302123317/http://www.boomsbeat.com/articles/153/20140127/50-interesting-facts-about-rihanna.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=|first=|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GGidBbtrM08|title=2005 Rihanna Interview|work=|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=|accessdate=2016-02-20|archive-date=2016-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160606035419/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GGidBbtrM08|dead-url=no}}</ref>同年，蕾哈娜与卡尔·斯特肯与埃文·罗杰斯的製作公司Syndicated Rhythm Productions签约。<ref name="TheGuardian1"/>

蕾哈娜的样本唱片也傳給了[[Def_Jam唱片公司|Def Jam唱片公司]]。公司的[[A&R|A&R]]杰·布朗是最早听到样本的人之一。布朗将样本放给饶舌歌手[[Jay_Z|Jay Z]]听。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.universalmusic.com/corporate/detail/231|title=THE ISLAND DEF JAM MUSIC GROUP APPOINTS SHAWN "JAY-Z" CARTER TO PRESIDENT & CEO, DEF JAM RECORDINGS|publisher=[[环球唱片|Universal Music Group]]|date=2004-12-08|accessdate=2015-02-22|archive-date=2015-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150317183153/http://www.universalmusic.com/corporate/detail/231|dead-url=no}}</ref>Jay Z在听完歌曲《[[百聽不厭|百聽不厭]]》后表示“这首歌曲对她来说难度太大了，（对于一个新艺人来说）很难达到这种水平。我不签歌曲，我只签艺人。”<ref name="Jay-ZPicks">{{cite web|last=Reid|first=Shaheem|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/yhif/jayz_picks/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110830053302/http://www.mtv.com/news/yhif/jayz_picks/|archivedate=2011-08-30|title=Jay-Z's Picks: Teairra Mari, Rihanna, Ne-Yo|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2011-09-24}}</ref>虽然感到怀疑，但之后，Jay Z仍邀请蕾哈娜去唱片公司试音。2005年年初，蕾哈娜在纽约的Def Jam唱片公司总部试音，在那里，Jay Z将她介绍给了音乐大师[[L·A·瑞德|L·A·瑞德]]。<ref name="TheGuardian1"/><ref name="USAToday1">{{cite news|last=Jones|first=Steve|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2005-08-01-otv-rihanna_x.htm|title=Rihanna has her day in the sun|work=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|date=2005-08-01|accessdate=2009-05-23|archive-date=2012-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120913193736/http://www.usatoday.com/life/music/news/2005-08-01-otv-rihanna_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>试音中，蕾哈娜唱了[[惠特妮·休斯顿|惠特妮·休斯顿]]版的《[[For_the_Love_of_You|For the Love of You]]》与她之前的样本《百聽不厭》和《{{lang|en|The Last Time}}》。<ref name="TheGuardian1"/>在她表演完《百聽不厭》之后，Jay Z很确信要签下这名歌手。<ref name="Jay-ZPicks"/>而瑞德在听完歌曲之后甚至告诉Jay Z，除非合同签下，不然不要让蕾哈娜离开大楼。<ref name=Ried17Rih>{{cite web|last=Reid|first=Antonio|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/magazine-feature/6836012/la-reid-on-meeting-rihanna-for-first-time-jay-z-beyonce|date=2016-01-07|title=L.A. Reid Recalls Meeting 17-Year-Old Rihanna for the First Time: Exclusive Memoir Excerpt|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=2016-02-19|archive-date=2016-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160209100755/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/magazine-feature/6836012/la-reid-on-meeting-rihanna-for-first-time-jay-z-beyonce|dead-url=no}}</ref>瑞德让Jay Z及其团队说服蕾哈娜签下6张专辑的合约。而为了防止蕾哈娜中途签下别的公司，蕾哈娜在Jay Z办公室驻守到了凌晨三点签约事宜结束。<ref name="Jay-ZPicks"/>
签约之后，蕾哈娜取消了其他公司的试音，并从巴巴多斯迁居美国，住在罗杰斯家。<ref name="RollingStone1">{{cite news|last=Eells|first=Josh|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/rihanna-queen-of-pain-rolling-stones-2011-cover-story-20110606?page=5|title=Rihanna, Queen of Pain: Rolling Stone's 2011 Cover Story|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]|date=2011-06-01|accessdate=2011-07-20|archive-date=2011-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111014184549/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/rihanna-queen-of-pain-rolling-stones-2011-cover-story-20110606?page=5|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===2005年–2006年：《太陽之歌》与《娜妹天下》===
{{Quote box|width=25em|align=right|quote=“想象与创造力，这是我音乐创作的源泉。（我）富有创造性，思考着一些我亲身经历的抑或我观察的其他人经历的状况。虽然我不敢说五年后我会在哪里看见我自己，但我敢说，在五年之中，我会尽我最大努力去做最成功的艺人。（我希望）以‘蕾哈娜’之名被人们记住，以从巴巴多斯到这里来享誉全球的艺人被人们记住，以我自己（的名义）被人们记住。我是真心对待自己的音乐事业的，所以我希望人们能了解这一点并因此欣赏我。”|source=—蕾哈娜第一次接受MTV新闻采访。<ref>{{cite news|last=Jones|first=Steve|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1627016/rihanna-plotted-her-path-to-success-in-first-mtv-news-interview/|title=Rihanna Plotted Her Path To Success In First MTV News Interview|work=[[音樂電視網|MTV]]|date=2009-11-21|accessdate=2016-02-17|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328050240/http://www.mtv.com/news/1627016/rihanna-plotted-her-path-to-success-in-first-mtv-news-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
}}
簽約後不久，Jay Z及其團隊開始著手準備蕾哈娜的首張錄音室專輯。<ref name=Ried17Rih/>蕾哈娜和一些不同的制作人，如羅傑斯以及他的制作搭档卡尔·斯特肯，一起制作这张专辑。<ref name="SlantMag1">{{cite news |url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/rihanna-music-of-the-sun/619 |title=Rihanna: Music Of The Sun {{!}} Music Review |last=Cinquemani |first=Sal |date=2005-08-31 |work=[[偏锋杂志|Slant Magazine]] |accessdate=2009-05-29 |archive-date=2010-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101112194905/http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/rihanna-music-of-the-sun/619 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在专辑制作完成后，由于制作团队认为，《百聽不厭》是最适合夏日发行的歌曲。因此，《百聽不厭》被选为了专辑的首张单曲。<ref name="SingUni">{{cite news|last=Kawashima|first=Dale|url=http://singeruniverse.com/rihanna.htm|title=Special Interview (2005): Rihanna Tells How She Got Started, Getting Her Label Deal, And Her First Album|work=Singer Universe|date=|accessdate=2016-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225150503/http://singeruniverse.com/rihanna.htm|archive-date=2016-02-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2005年5月，《百聽不厭》正式发行，在全球许多榜单取得了较大的成功，在15个国家的榜单进入了前5名。在美国，歌曲在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《公告牌》百强单曲榜]]最高排位取得了第2名。<ref name="BillChartS">{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=rihanna|chart=all}}|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080728075941/{{BillboardURLbyName|artist=rihanna|chart=all}}|archivedate=2008-07-28|title= Artist Chart History — Rihanna|work=Billboard|accessdate=2009-02-06}}</ref>

蕾哈娜的首张录音室专辑《[[太陽之歌_(專輯)|太陽之歌]]》于2005年8月正式发行。专辑空降[[告示牌二百强专辑榜|《公告牌》二百强专辑榜]]第10名。之后，专辑以500,000份销售单元被[[美国唱片工业协会|美国唱片工业协会]]认证为金唱片。<ref name="RIAA-albums">{{cite web|url=https://www.riaa.com/?s=Rihanna |title=RIAA — Gold & Platinum |publisher=Recording Industry Association of America |accessdate=2017-02-09}}</ref>专辑的第二支单曲《[[討愛|討愛]]》不如第一支单曲成功，但也在澳大利亚、爱尔兰和新西兰进入了榜单前10。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1508016/20050819/rihanna.jhtml |title=Rihanna Insists She's Got What You Need In 'Pon De Replay' Follow-Up |last=Tecson |first=Brandee |date=2005-08-19 |publisher=MTV News |accessdate=2009-06-02 |archive-date=2009-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090306212203/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1508016/20050819/rihanna.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
在进行音乐工作的同时，蕾哈娜也开始尝试进入其它产业。她[[友情客串|友情客串]]了2006年电影《[[魅力四射3|魅力四射3]]》。<ref name="BringsOnActing">{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1512953/20051103/story.jhtml |title=Rihanna Brings On Acting Career With New 'Bring It On' Flick |last=Tecson |first=Brandee J. |date=2005-11-03 |publisher=MTV News |accessdate=2009-05-23 |archive-date=2009-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104093324/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1512953/20051103/story.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[File:RihannaJingle_Ball_cropped.jpg|thumb]]表演。]]

在《太陽之歌》发行一个月后，蕾哈娜开始着手准备自己的第二张录音室专辑。<ref name="HerRockSide">{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1524534/20060217/rihanna.jhtml |title=Rihanna Getting In Touch With Her Rock Side For Next LP |last=Tecson |first=Brandee J. |date=2006-02-22 |publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]] |accessdate=2009-06-02 |archive-date=2008-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081226231134/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1524534/20060217/rihanna.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>2006年4月，她的第二张录音室专辑《[[娜妹天下|娜妹天下]]》发行。<ref>{{cite web |url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=rihanna|chart=all}} |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080804183011/{{BillboardURLbyName|artist=rihanna|chart=all}} |archivedate=2008-08-04 |title=Billboard.com — Discography — Rihanna — A Girl Like Me |accessdate=2009-05-27 |work=Billboard }}</ref>《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》的编辑巴里·沃尔特斯认为，《娜妹天下》比《太陽之歌》更加讨喜。<ref>{{cite news|last=Walters|first=Barry|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/albumreviews/a-girl-like-me-20060526|title=Rihanna – A Girl like Me|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]|publisher=[[Jann_Wenner|Jann Wenner]]|accessdate=2012-01-02|archive-date=2008-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080212151010/http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/album/9941006/a_girl_like_me|dead-url=no}}</ref>专辑取得了全球性的商业成功，在13个国家进入了榜单前10名。在加拿大，专辑取得了冠军，在英国，专辑最高排位第5名。在美国，专辑首周取得了115,000份销售单元，在二百强专辑榜最高排位第5名。<ref name="RIAA-albums"/><ref name="acharts">{{cite web |url=http://acharts.us/album/14395 |title=Rihanna – A Girl like Me – Music Charts |accessdate=2009-08-21 |work=αCharts.us |archive-date=2012-08-16 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69xMoITOd?url=http://acharts.us/album/14395 |dead-url=no }}</ref>专辑在美国取得1,000,000份销售单元后，被美国唱片工业协会认证为了白金唱片。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5793204/rihanna-hits-10-million-in-us-album-sales|title=Rihanna Hits 10 Million in U.S. Album Sales|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=2013-11-16|accessdate=2016-08-03|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|archive-date=2015-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151221193719/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/5793204/rihanna-hits-10-million-in-us-album-sales|dead-url=no}}</ref>专辑的首张单曲，《[[求救訊號_(歌曲)|求救訊號]]》全球走红，在11个国家进入了榜单前5名。在美国和澳大利亚，歌曲取得了冠军。<ref name="SOSAcharts">{{cite news |url=http://acharts.us/song/7805 |title=Rihanna – SOS – Music Charts |work=[[Music_Charts|Music Charts]] |accessdate=2009-08-24 |archive-date=2009-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090224055410/http://acharts.us/song/7805 |dead-url=no }}</ref>专辑的第二张单曲《[[罪愛_(歌曲)|罪愛]]》在18个国家进入了榜单前10名，在加拿大和瑞士夺冠。<ref name="UnfaithfulAcharts">{{cite news |url=http://acharts.us/song/8433 |title=Rihanna – Unfaithful – Music Charts |work=[[Music_Charts|Music Charts]] |accessdate=2009-08-24 |archive-date=2008-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227054034/http://acharts.us/song/8433 |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，专辑还发行了《[[乘著風|乘著風]]》和《[[暫時停止|暫時停止]]》两支单曲。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1535606/20060705/rihanna.jhtml |title=Rihanna Lets Fans Be Her Guide, Selects Summer Jam 'We Ride' As Next Single |last=Moss |first=Corey |date=2006-07-06 |publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]] |accessdate=2009-06-02 |archive-date=2009-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104105706/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1535606/20060705/rihanna.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Katie Hasty, [http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1054358/mims-puts-the-hot-in-the-hot-100-at-no-1 "Mims Puts The 'Hot' In The Hot 100 At No. 1"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1054358/mims-puts-the-hot-in-the-hot-100-at-no-1 |date=20161219042841 }}, ''Billboard'', March 1, 2007</ref>

===2007年–2009年：《娜妹好壞》与《限制級》===
2007年年初，蕾哈娜开始制作第3张录音室专辑《[[娜妹好坏|娜妹好坏]]》。<ref name="neyo lessons">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1553347/rihanna-gets-voice-lessons-from-ne-yo-for-fresh-uptempo-new-tracks/|title=Rihanna Gets Voice Lessons From Ne-Yo For 'Fresh, Uptempo' New Tracks|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|last=Moss|first=Corey|date=2007-02-27|accessdate=2013-09-04|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915210708/http://www.mtv.com/news/1553347/rihanna-gets-voice-lessons-from-ne-yo-for-fresh-uptempo-new-tracks/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在制作人[[提姆巴蘭|提姆巴蘭]]、[[崔西·斯图尔特|崔西·斯图尔特]]与[[肖恩·加勒特|肖恩·加勒特]]的帮助下，蕾哈娜将自己的音乐风格转为快节奏舞曲。<ref name="LosesGoodImage">{{cite web |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1558496/20070501/rihanna.jhtml |title=Rihanna Loses Good Girl Image, Thanks To Jay-Z, Justin, Timbaland, Ne-Yo |last1=Reid |first1=Shaheem |last2=Richard |first2=Yasmine |date=2007-05-02 |publisher=MTV News |accessdate=2009-06-01 |archive-date=2009-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220135412/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1558496/20070501/rihanna.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VoiceLessons">{{Cite news |last=Moss |first=Corey |title=Rihanna Gets Voice Lessons From Ne-Yo For 'Fresh, Uptempo' New Tracks |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1553347/20070226/rihanna.jhtml |publisher=MTV News |date=2006-02-27 |accessdate=2012-09-27 |archive-date=2009-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104042919/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1553347/20070226/rihanna.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>2007年5月，专辑正式发行，在巴西、加拿大、爱尔兰和英国取得了冠军，在美国和澳大利亚取得了亚军，<ref name="GGGBcharts">{{cite news |url=http://acharts.us/album/26334 |title=Rihanna – Good Girl Gone Bad – Music Charts |work=[[Music_Charts|Music Charts]] |accessdate=2009-08-24 |archive-date=2009-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090204193904/http://acharts.us/album/26334 |dead-url=no }}</ref>也获得了乐评的普遍好评。<ref name="metacritic">{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/artists/rihanna/goodgirlgonebad | title=Rihanna:Good Girl Gone Bad (2007): Reviews | publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | accessdate=2009-03-24 | archive-date=2009-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090226235849/http://www.metacritic.com/music/artists/rihanna/goodgirlgonebad | dead-url=no }}</ref>首张单曲《[[小雨傘|小雨傘]]》在十三個國家奪冠。在英國，歌曲甚至取得了連續十周冠軍。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://acharts.us/song/16150|title=Rihanna and Jay-Z – Umbrella – Music Charts|work=[[Music_Charts|Music Charts]]|accessdate=2009-08-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091004163344/http://acharts.us/song/16150|archivedate=2009-10-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1050626/rihanna-makes-it-10-weeks-atop-uk-singles-chart|title=Rihanna Makes It 10 Weeks Atop UK Singles Chart|last=Sexton|first=Paul|date=2007-07-23|work=Billboard|accessdate=2009-02-08|archive-date=2018-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180716230824/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1050626/rihanna-makes-it-10-weeks-atop-uk-singles-chart|dead-url=no}}</ref>這張單曲在全球總共取得了660万份銷量，是蕾哈娜第一張列入[[畅销单曲列表|世界暢銷單曲清單]]的單曲。<ref name="ifpi2007">{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/DMR2008.pdf|title=Top 10 Global Digital Singles 2007|publisher=[[國際唱片業協會|International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]]|page=6|accessdate=2010-11-13|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915210859/http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/DMR2008.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/DMR2008.pdf|title=Top 10 Digital Songs 2009|date=2012-02-15|work=IFPI|accessdate=2017-02-09|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915210859/http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/DMR2008.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌曲《[[逍遙遊_(歌曲)|逍遙遊]]》和《[[我恨我愛你|我恨我愛你]]》隨後也發行了單曲，後者在全球大獲成功。為了宣傳專輯，蕾哈娜在2007年9月開啟了[[娜妹好壞巡迴演唱會|娜妹好壞巡迴演唱會]]，在全球進行了80場演出。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtvasia.com/Review/Event/E20081117001729.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130711222550/http://m/ |archivedate=2013-07-11 |title=Rihanna's Good Girl Gone Bad Tour |last=Leong |first=Cheryl |date=2008-11-13 |work=[[MTV_Southeast_Asia|MTV Southeast Asia]] |accessdate=2009-05-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>在[[第50届格莱美奖|第50届格莱美奖]]上，蕾哈娜獲得了多項提名。最終，《小雨傘》獲得了[[格莱美奖最佳饶舌/演唱合作|格莱美奖最佳饶舌/演唱合作]]，成為蕾哈娜職業生涯第一座格莱美奖。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1567466_20010832_20177185,00.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080212091054/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1567466_20010832_20177185,00.html|archivedate=2008-02-12|title=The 2008 Grammy Winners Are...|date=2008-02-08|work=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2009-04-23}}</ref>

