整個2000年代末，蕾哈娜都在尋求自己音樂上與個人形象上的轉型。<ref>{{cite web|last=Emina|first=Kyle|url=http://dailytrojan.com/2011/11/28/rihanna-revitalizes-tired-musical-style/|title=Rihanna revitalizes tired musical style|publisher=|date=2011-11-28|accessdate=2015-10-09|archive-date=2016-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160111202157/http://dailytrojan.com/2011/11/28/rihanna-revitalizes-tired-musical-style/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2008年，蕾哈娜與[[肯伊·威斯特|肯伊·威斯特]]、[[卢普·菲亚斯科|卢普·菲亚斯科]]和[[N.E.R.D|N.E.R.D]]共同在[[暗中發光巡迴演唱會|暗中發光巡迴演唱會]]表演。<ref name="mtv">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1580653/20080130/west_kanye.jhtml|title=Kanye West's Glow In The Dark Tour Will Feature Rihanna, Lupe Fiasco, N.E.R.D.|last=Rodriguez|first=Jayson|publisher=MTV News|date=2008-01-30|accessdate=2008-11-11|archive-date=2008-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081228075443/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1580653/20080130/west_kanye.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月，《娜妹好壞》的改版《[[娜妹好壞_(超級好樣版)|娜妹好壞 (超級好樣版)]]》發行。改版專輯收錄了三首新歌曲：《[[恐怖社区_(歌曲)|恐怖社区]]》、《[[謝幕_(蕾哈娜歌曲)|謝幕]]》以及與[[魔力紅|魔力紅]]合作的《[[如果不能再見你一面|如果不能再見你一面]]》，這些歌曲在全球各地榜單都取得了較高的排位。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://acharts.us/song/34994 |title=Rihanna – Take A Bow – Music Charts |publisher=Acharts.us |accessdate=2008-10-23 |archive-date=2012-04-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66l9Cw3fW?url=http://acharts.us/song/34994 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://acharts.us/song/35570 |title=Maroon 5 and Rihanna – If I Never See Your Face Again – Music Charts |publisher=Acharts.us |accessdate=2008-10-23 |archive-date=2012-04-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66l9DzNkz?url=http://acharts.us/song/35570 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://acharts.us/song/36121 |title=Rihanna – Disturbia – Music Charts |publisher=Acharts.us |accessdate=2008-10-23 |archive-date=2008-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080923191553/http://acharts.us/song/36121 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《娜妹好壞》及其改版專輯在美國共取得了280萬份銷量，獲得了美國唱片工業協會二白金認證，是迄今為止蕾哈娜在美國銷量最高的一張專輯。<ref name="RIAA-albums"/><ref name="May 2013 Sales">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1565445/rihanna-earns-sixth-million-selling-album|title=Rihanna Earns Sixth Million-Selling Album|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2013-05-30|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915210924/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/1565445/rihanna-earns-sixth-million-selling-album|dead-url=no}}</ref>專輯在全球則取得了超過700萬份銷量。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/beyonc-lady-gaga-rihanna-albums-to-hit-shelves-november-23-1821889.html|title=Beyoncé, Lady Gaga, Rihanna albums to hit shelves November 23|date=2009-11-17|location=London|work=The Independent|accessdate=2017-02-09|archive-date=2011-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111108005015/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/news/beyonc-lady-gaga-rihanna-albums-to-hit-shelves-november-23-1821889.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月，為支援抗癌活動[[对抗癌症|对抗癌症]]，蕾哈娜和一眾女歌手錄製了慈善單曲《[[站起来！|站起来！]]》。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1593043/20080819/carey_mariah.jhtml |title=Mariah Carey, Beyoncé, Rihanna, Fergie, Miley Cyrus, More Collaborate On Cancer Benefit Single |last=Kaufman |first=Gil |date=2008-08-19 |publisher=MTV |accessdate=2009-05-14 |archive-date=2010-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101224015644/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1593043/20080819/carey_mariah.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>11月，蕾哈娜和[[T.I.|T.I.]]合作演唱的歌曲《[[Live_Your_Life_(T.I.歌曲)|Live Your Life]]》發佈，在百強單曲榜奪冠。2008年末，蕾哈娜被《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》評為“年度天后”。<ref>{{cite news|title=Rihanna: Diva of the year|url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2008/12/29/rihanna-diva-of/|work=Entertainment Weekly|last=Watson|first=Margeaux|date=2008-12-29|accessdate=2014-03-05|archive-date=2013-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202231635/http://music-mix.ew.com/2008/12/29/rihanna-diva-of/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2009年1月，《娜妹好壞》的混音版專輯《[[娜妹好壞混音特輯|娜妹好壞混音特輯]]》發佈。

