首張單曲《[[萬中選一_(歌曲)|萬中選一]]》在十五個國家奪冠，包括英美兩國。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/canadian-hot-100/2010-10-02|title=Billboard Canadian Hot 100: Week of October 2, 2010|work=Billboard|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2015-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151109084441/http://www.billboard.com/charts/canadian-hot-100/2010-10-02|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Rihanna&titel=Only+Girl+%28In+The+World%29&cat=s|title=Rihanna — Only Girl (In The World)|publisher=australian-charts.com|accessdate=2010-11-27|archive-date=2016-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160324081525/http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Rihanna&titel=Only+Girl+%28In+The+World%29&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2010-11-13/|title=Archive Chart|publisher=theofficialcharts.com|accessdate=2010-11-27|archive-date=2012-06-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68AId70iq?url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2010-11-13/|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二張單曲《[[呼喊我的名|呼喊我的名]]》與[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]合作，在英美兩國同樣取得了冠軍。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2010/11/11/rihanna-whats-my-name-no-1-billboard-hot-100/ |title=Rihanna's 'What's My Name?' jumps to No. 1 on Billboard Hot 100 chart |work=Entertainment Weekly |last=Wete |first=Brad |accessdate=2010-11-11 |archive-date=2012-06-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68AIeiISA?url=http://music-mix.ew.com/2010/11/11/rihanna-whats-my-name-no-1-billboard-hot-100/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>第三張單曲《[[禁忌遊戲|禁忌遊戲]]》在發行布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯混音版之後，在美國奪冠。《禁忌遊戲》是蕾哈娜第十張美國冠軍單曲，其奪冠標誌著蕾哈娜成為最快取得十張冠軍單曲的藝人。<ref name="'S&M'Reigns">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/471954/rihannas-sm-reigns-on-hot-100-lady-gagas-judas-debuts|title=Rihanna's 'S&M' Reigns on Hot 100, Lady Gaga's 'Judas' Debuts|work=Billboard|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2011-04-20|accessdate=2012-01-29|archive-date=2016-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219034043/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/471954/rihannas-sm-reigns-on-hot-100-lady-gagas-judas-debuts|dead-url=no}}</ref>

