p://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/the-juice/473127/rihanna-to-kick-off-north-american-loud-tour-in-june | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/rihanna/news/o2-arena-record/| title=Rihanna Breaks O2 Arena Record With Final 'Loud' Tour Gig| accessdate=2011-12-22| date=2012-02-15| work=Capital FM| archive-date=2012-11-22| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121122134155/http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/rihanna/news/o2-arena-record/| dead-url=no}}</ref>在伦敦的最后三场演出最后被录制成了蕾哈娜第2张现场影视专辑《[[倫敦O2演唱會|倫敦O<sub>2</sub>演唱會]]》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/rihanna/news/loud-tour-live-dvd/|title=Rihanna To Film Final Three Shows Of 'Loud' Tour For Live DVD|publisher=[[首都電臺_(電臺網)|首都電臺]]|date=2011-12-19|accessdate=2013-01-01|archive-date=2013-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130730091104/http://www.capitalfm.com/artists/rihanna/news/loud-tour-live-dvd/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/dp/B00AAQ7LP6?keywords=loud+tour|title=Rihanna: Loud Tour Live at the O2 (2012)|publisher=[[亞馬遜公司|Amazon.com]]|date=2013-01-23|accessdate=2012-12-18}}</ref>巡演是2011年票房收入第7高的巡演之一。<ref name="PSP">{{cite web |url=http://www.pollstarpro.com/charts/2011YearEndTop25WorldwideTours.pdf |title=Pollstar: Top 25 Worldwide Tours (1/1/2011 – 12/31/2011) |date=2011-12-28 |work=Pollstar |accessdate=2011-12-29 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/64I05wGYs?url=http://www.pollstarpro.com/charts/2011YearEndTop25WorldwideTours.pdf |archivedate=2011-12-29 |deadurl=yes }}</ref> 

蕾哈娜的第6张录音室专辑《[[娜样说|娜样说]]》于2011年11月发行。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a345070/rihanna-unveils-new-album-talk-that-talk-cover.html | title=Rihanna unveils new album 'Talk That Talk' cover | accessdate=2011-10-25 | author=Fowler, Tara | date=2011-10-11 | work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] | archive-date=2011-10-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028174136/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a345070/rihanna-unveils-new-album-talk-that-talk-cover.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>专辑以198,000份销量空降二百强专辑榜季军。<ref>{{cite web|author1=Caulfield, Keith|title=Michael Buble Bests Nickelback, Rihanna on Billboard 200|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/464922/michael-buble-bests-nickelback-rihanna-on-billboard-200|publisher=Nielsen Business Media|accessdate=2017-02-09|archive-date=2018-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181114075106/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/464922/michael-buble-bests-nickelback-rihanna-on-billboard-200|dead-url=no}}</ref>在英国则以163,000份首周销量空降冠军。专辑的首张单曲《[[找到愛|找到愛]]》在全球27国夺冠，在超过30个国家进入了榜单前10，打破了多项记录。<ref name="wflcharts">{{cite news |url=http://acharts.us/song/65699 |title=Rihanna Calvin Harris — We Found Love |work=[[Music_Charts|Music Charts]] |accessdate=2012-06-08 |archive-date=2012-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614114822/http://acharts.us/song/65699 |dead-url=no }}</ref>专辑在百强单曲榜取得了不连续的十周冠军，是蕾哈娜夺冠周数最长的单曲，也是2011年全年夺冠周数最长的单曲。<ref name="wflcharts2">{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/465364/rihannas-found-her-way-back-to-hot-100-summit|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|title=Rihanna's 'Found' Her Way Back to Hot 100 Summit|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2011-11-02|accessdate=2012-09-07|archive-date=2018-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203203838/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/465364/rihannas-found-her-way-back-to-hot-100-summit|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="wflcharts3">{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/464691/rihannas-love-her-longest-leading-hot-100-no-1|work=Billboard|title=Rihanna's 'Love' Her Longest-Leading Hot 100 No. 1|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2011-12-21|accessdate=2012-09-07|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915210620/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/464691/rihannas-love-her-longest-leading-hot-100-no-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[你是唯一|你是唯一]]》、《[[娜樣說_(蕾哈娜歌曲)|娜樣說]]》分别作为专辑的第2张和第3张单曲发行。第5张单曲《[[你去哪了|你去哪了]]》取得了全球成功，在美国最高排位第5，在英国最高排位第6。<ref name="USHot100July7Peak">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100/2012-07-07|title=The Hot 100: Week of July 7, 2012|work=Billboard|date=2012-07-07|accessdate=2015-10-13|archive-date=2015-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913035100/http://www.billboard.com/charts/hot-100/2012-07-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="WHYBPeakUK">{{cite web|url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2012-05-26/|title=Archive Chart|publisher=[[官方榜单公司|The Official Charts Company]]|date=2012-07-07|accessdate=2012-05-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130204023628/http://www.theofficialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/1/2012-05-26/|archivedate=2013-02-04}}</ref>与[[ASAP_Rocky|ASAP Rocky]]合作的《[[驕傲自大（愛呀）|驕傲自大（愛呀）]]》则是专辑的第6张单曲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rap-up.com/2012/09/04/new-music-rihanna-f-asap-rocky-cockiness-love-it-remix/#more-134429 |title=New Music: Rihanna f/ A$AP Rocky – 'Cockiness (Remix)' |publisher=Rap-Up.com |accessdate=2012-10-24 |archive-date=2012-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022101525/http://www.rap-up.com/2012/09/04/new-music-rihanna-f-asap-rocky-cockiness-love-it-remix/#more-134429 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

