 'didn't expect negative Chris Brown duet reaction' | accessdate=2012-06-14 | author=Corner, Lewis | date=2012-06-06 | work=[[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] | archive-date=2012-06-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120615011849/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a385634/rihanna-didnt-expect-negative-chris-brown-duet-reaction.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>9月，《[[找到愛_(影片)|找到愛]]》獲得了[[MTV音樂錄影帶大獎年度影片|MTV音樂錄影帶大獎年度影片]]，使蕾哈娜成為第一個兩次獲得此殊榮的藝人。<ref name="2012 VMA">{{cite web|url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/awards/rihanna-one-direction-top-vmas-022745243.html|title=Rihanna, One Direction Top VMAs|publisher=[[雅虎|Yahoo!]]|date=2012-09-06|accessdate=2012-09-07|archive-date=2012-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120911032420/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/awards/rihanna-one-direction-top-vmas-022745243.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

