ef>首张单曲《[[璀鑽_(蕾哈娜歌曲)|璀鑽]]》在全球超过20个国家夺冠。<ref name="Trust">{{Cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474056/rihannas-diamonds-shines-atop-hot-100|work=Billboard|title=Rihanna's 'Diamonds' Shines Atop Hot 100|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2012-11-21|accessdate=2012-11-21|archive-date=2018-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180915210614/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/474056/rihannas-diamonds-shines-atop-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>第二张单曲《[[留下|留下]]》与[[米奇·艾可|米奇·艾可]]合作，在超过20个国家进入了榜单前5名。<ref>{{cite web|last=Trust|first=Gary|title=Baauer's 'Harlem Shake' Debuts Atop Revamped Hot 100|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/chart-alert/1549395/baauers-harlem-shake-debuts-atop-revamped-hot-100|work=Billboard|accessdate=2013-02-21|location=New York, NY|date=2013-02-21|archive-date=2013-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130221232058/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/chart-alert/1549395/baauers-harlem-shake-debuts-atop-revamped-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年2月的[[第55届格莱美奖|第55届格莱美奖]]，蕾哈娜以《找到爱》的音乐录影带赢得了最佳音乐录影短片。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/early-grammy-winners-include-rihanna-jay-z-and-kanye-west-20130210|title=Early Grammy Winners Include Rihanna, Jay-Z and Kanye West|work=Rolling Stone|date=2013-02-10|accessdate=2013-02-11|archive-date=2013-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213201257/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/early-grammy-winners-include-rihanna-jay-z-and-kanye-west-20130210|dead-url=no}}</ref>同月，英国[[官方榜单公司|官方榜单公司]]宣布，蕾哈娜2012年在英国共取得了3,868,000份唱片销量，是[[2013年全英音乐奖|2013年全英音乐奖]]被提名艺人中销量最高的艺人。<ref name="officialcharts.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-brit-awards-2013-the-real-winners-revealed-1869/|title=The BRIT Awards 2013: The biggest selling nominees revealed|publisher=Official Charts Company|date=2013-02-20|accessdate=2013-02-20|archive-date=2013-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130224025316/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-brit-awards-2013-the-real-winners-revealed-1869/|dead-url=no}}</ref>为宣传专辑，蕾哈娜于3月开启了[[璀鑽世界巡迴演唱會|璀鑽世界巡迴演唱會]]。<ref>{{cite web|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|title=Rihanna Unveils Diamonds Tour Dates After Big VMA Night|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1693402/rihanna-tour-dates-vma-2012.jhtml|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2012-09-09|date=2012-09-07|archive-date=2012-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120909225914/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1693402/rihanna-tour-dates-vma-2012.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月，蕾哈娜在当月发行的电影《[[大明星世界末日|大明星世界末日]]》参演自己本人一角。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a469803/this-is-the-end-rihanna-doesnt-make-it-in-red-band-trailer.html|title='This Is the End': Rihanna doesn't make it in red band trailer|work=Digital Spy|date=2013-04-02|accessdate=2013-04-02|archive-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130420025002/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/movies/news/a469803/this-is-the-end-rihanna-doesnt-make-it-in-red-band-trailer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>同月，蕾哈娜客串[[威尔_(饶舌歌手)|威尔]]歌曲《[[Bad_(威爾歌曲)|Bad]]》的混音版本发行。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/bad-remix-feat.-rihanna/id657264827?i=657264828|title=iTunes Music – Bad [Remix] (feat. Rihanna) – Single by Wale|publisher=iTunes Store|date=2013-06-05|accessdate=2013-06-03|archive-date=2015-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701061112/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/bad-remix-feat.-rihanna/id657264827?i=657264828|dead-url=no}}</ref>

10月，阿姆与蕾哈娜再次合作，推出了新单曲《[[怪獸_(阿姆歌曲)|怪獸]]》。歌曲在英国夺冠，使蕾哈娜连续七年在该国都有冠军单曲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/eminem-and-rihanna-deny-one-direction-their-fourth-number-1-2585/ |title=Eminem and Rihanna deny One Direction their fourth Number 1 |publisher=Officialcharts.com |accessdate=2014-01-19 |archive-date=2014-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031011130/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/eminem-and-rihanna-deny-one-direction-their-fourth-number-1-2585/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>歌曲在美国亦夺冠，是蕾哈娜第13张冠军单曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5820081/eminem-rihanna-rule-hot-100-with-the-monster|title=Eminem, Rihanna Rule Hot 100 With 'The Monster'|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=Nielson Soundscan, Inc|first=Gary|last=Trust|date=2013-12-11|accessdate=2013-12-11|archive-date=2013-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131222014903/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5820081/eminem-rihanna-rule-hot-100-with-the-monster|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[第57届格莱美奖|第57届格莱美奖]]中，歌曲赢得了最佳饶舌/演唱合作。2014年年初，蕾哈娜还与夏奇拉合作，发布了单曲《[[無法忘記你|無法忘記你]]》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/latin-notas/5869585/shakira-rihanna-team-up-on-cant-remember-to-forget-you-listen|title=Shakira, Rihanna Team Up On 'Can't Remember To Forget You': Listen|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|date=2014-01-13|accessdate=2014-04-21|archive-date=2018-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726062501/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/latin-notas/5869585/shakira-rihanna-team-up-on-cant-remember-to-forget-you-listen|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月，蕾哈娜正式离开Def Jam唱片，与[[Roc_Nation|Roc Nation]]签下了完整合同。<ref name=label>{{cite news|last=Nostro|first=Lauren|title=Rihanna Has Left Def Jam and Signed to Jay Z's Roc Nation Label|url=http://www.complex.com/music/2014/05/rihanna-roc-nation-management-label-deal|accessdate=2014-05-05|newspaper=Complex|date=2014-05-05|archive-date=2019-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430122541/https://www.complex.com/music/2014/05/rihanna-roc-nation-management-label-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>

