2014年开始就有消息指蕾哈娜正着手制作第8张录音室专辑。<ref>{{cite web |last=Lindner |first=Emilee |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1719931/most-anticipated-pop-albums-2014.jhtml |title=Taylor Swift, Rihanna Top Most Anticipated Pop Albums Of 2014 |publisher=MTV |date=2014-01-07 |accessdate=2014-01-19 |archive-date=2014-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140127050651/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1719931/most-anticipated-pop-albums-2014.jhtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Vokes-Dudgeon|first1=Sophie|title=Rihanna Unveils Artwork for New Album Anti, Invites Guests to Touch the Work|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/rihanna-unveils-artwork-for-new-album-anti-encourages-touching-2015810|website=US Magazine|accessdate=2015-10-08|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008205000/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/rihanna-unveils-artwork-for-new-album-anti-encourages-touching-2015810|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年1月，蕾哈娜发行了单曲《[[FourFiveSeconds|FourFiveSeconds]]》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2058811/rihanna-four-five-seconds/|title=Rihanna Dropped Her New Song With Kanye And Paul McCartney—Hear 'FourFiveSeconds'|publisher=[[MTV_News|MTV News]]|last=White|first=Caitlin|date=2015-01-25|accessdate=2015-04-03|archive-date=2019-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190515111007/http://www.mtv.com/news/2058811/rihanna-four-five-seconds/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后又相继发布了《[[Bitch_Better_Have_My_Money|Bitch Better Have My Money]]》和《[[American_Oxygen|American Oxygen]]》两支单曲。<ref>{{cite web|last=Anderson|first=Stacey|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6516868/rihanna-debuts-bitch-better-have-my-money-at-iheartradio-awards|title=Rihanna Debuts 'Bitch Better Have My Money' at iHeartRadio Awards|work=Billboard|date=2015-03-29|accessdate=2015-04-03|archive-date=2019-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217183414/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6516868/rihanna-debuts-bitch-better-have-my-money-at-iheartradio-awards|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://time.com/3771826/rihanna-american-oxygen-tidal-jay-z-beyonce-march-madness-ncaa-basketball/ | work=Time | title=Rihanna Debuts Soulful 'American Oxygen' on Tidal | date=2015-04-06 | accessdate=2017-02-09 | archive-date=2016-08-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830042134/http://time.com/3771826/rihanna-american-oxygen-tidal-jay-z-beyonce-march-madness-ncaa-basketball/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.yahoo.com/music/rihanna-debuts-american-oxygen-slams-rfra-at-115594321481.html|title=Rihanna Debuts 'American Oxygen,’ Slams RFRA at March Madness Fest|date=2015-04-05|work=yahoo.com|accessdate=2017-02-09|archive-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807120125/https://www.yahoo.com/music/rihanna-debuts-american-oxygen-slams-rfra-at-115594321481.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，这些单曲均未正式收录于第8张录音室专辑中。同年，蕾哈娜还参与了电影《[[疯狂外星人|疯狂外星人]]》的配音。<ref>{{cite news|last=Graser|first=Marc|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/rihanna-to-make-concept-album-for-dreamworks-animations-home-1201120819/|title=Rihanna to Make Concept Album for Upcoming Animated Movie|work=Variety|date=2014-02-25|accessdate=2014-04-23|archive-date=2014-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140509172650/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/rihanna-to-make-concept-album-for-dreamworks-animations-home-1201120819/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2月24日，由蕾哈娜演唱的电影主题曲《[[Towards_the_Sun_(歌曲)|Towards the Sun]]》发行。<ref>{{cite web|last=Lipshutz|first=Jason|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6480449/rihanna-towards-the-sun-single-home-soundtrack|title=Rihanna Releases 'Towards the Sun' Single From 'Home' Soundtrack|work=Billboard|date=2015-02-24|accessdate=2015-04-03|archive-date=2015-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401062841/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6480449/rihanna-towards-the-sun-single-home-soundtrack|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月1日，美国唱片工业协会宣