2009-05-28 |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2009-10-28 |archive-date=2014-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208023212/http://news-briefs.ew.com/2009/05/28/rihanna-may-tes/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>当日，布朗認罪，法庭判处布朗五年緩刑，並要求布朗与蕾哈娜的日常人身距離保持50碼（46米），在公开活动时距离可減少到10碼（9米）。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.tmz.com/2009/06/22/chris-brown-cops-plea-rihanna-assault/ |title=Chris Brown Cops Plea — No Jail Time |date=2009-06-22 |publisher=[[TMZ|TMZ.com]] |accessdate=2009-06-22 |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327111004/https://www.tmz.com/2009/06/22/chris-brown-cops-plea-rihanna-assault/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2011年2月，應布朗律師的要求，经蕾哈娜同意后，法官帕特里夏·史内格將限制令修改為“一級令”，允許两人在未來共同出席頒獎典禮。<ref>{{cite web|title=Chris Brown's Restraining Order Modified|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1658478/chris-brown-restraining-order-lifted.jhtml|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2012-02-13|author=Ryan J. Downey|date=2011-02-22|archive-date=2012-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120101053608/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1658478/chris-brown-restraining-order-lifted.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Pepey|first=Tracy|title=Rihanna's Restraining Order Against Chris Brown Lifted|url=http://www.ivillage.com/rihannas-restraining-order-against-chris-brown-lifted/1-a-325572|work=iVillage|accessdate=2012-02-13|date=2011-02-23|archive-date=2012-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024011713/http://www.ivillage.com/rihannas-restraining-order-against-chris-brown-lifted/1-a-325572|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2009年12月到2010年期间，蕾哈娜曾与[[洛杉矶道奇|洛杉矶道奇]]棒球运动员[[麥特·坎普|麥特·坎普]]交往。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/rihanna-confirms-los-angeles-dodger-star-matt-kemp-boyfriend-article-1.166359|title=Rihanna confirms Los Angeles Dodger star Matt Kemp is her 'boyfriend'|last=Everett|first=Cristina|accessdate=2014-09-29|date=2010-04-09|location=New York|work=Daily News|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007043846/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/rihanna-confirms-los-angeles-dodger-star-matt-kemp-boyfriend-article-1.166359|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后，蕾哈娜还和加拿大饶舌歌手[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]交往过一段时间。<ref>{{cite news|title=Drake Slams Chris Brown and Finally Admits He Dated Rihanna In New Interview|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/04/13/drake-slams-chris-brown_n_3075784.html|work=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-04-13|date=2013-06-06|first=Stephanie|last=Marcus|archive-date=2013-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130414072605/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/04/13/drake-slams-chris-brown_n_3075784.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年，不断有媒体报道称蕾哈娜已与克里斯·布朗复合。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://rapfix.mtv.com/2012/10/05/rihanna-chris-brown-road-to-friendship/|title=Rihanna And Chris Brown's Road To Friendship|publisher=MTV|date=2012-10-05|accessdate=2012-10-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007081402/http://rapfix.mtv.com/2012/10/05/rihanna-chris-brown-road-to-friendship/|archivedate=2012-10-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://rapfix.mtv.com/2012/10/05/chris-brown-loves-rihanna-karreuche-tran/|title=Chris Brown Loves Both Rihanna And Karreuche Tran|publisher=MTV|date=2012-10-05|accessdate=2012-10-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007081529/http://rapfix.mtv.com/2012/10/05/chris-brown-loves-rihanna-karreuche-tran/|archivedate=2012-10-07}}</ref>2013年1月，在接受《滚石》的采访中，蕾哈娜正式确认，尽管克里斯·布朗仍在家暴事件的观察期。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2012/09/24/us/ap-us-people-chris-brown.html|title=Judge Seeks More Review of Chris Brown's Probation|work=The New York Times|date=2012-09-24 |accessdate=2012-10-06}}</ref>但她已与布朗修复关系。<ref name="telegraph2013">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/9837484/Rihanna-breaks-silence-over-Chris-Brown-if-its-a-mistake-its-my-mistake.html|title=Rihanna breaks silence over Chris Brown: 'if it's a mistake, it's my mistake'|work=The Telegraph|accessdate=2013-01-31|date=2013-01-30|location=London|archive-date=2013-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130213013926/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/celebritynews/9837484/Rihanna-breaks-silence-over-Chris-Brown-if-its-a-mistake-its-my-mistake.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年5月，布朗宣布与蕾哈娜再次分手。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/chris-brown-confirms-rihanna-breakup-i-cant-focus-on-wife-ing-her-201365|title=Chris Brown Confirms Rihanna Breakup: "I Can't Focus on Wife-ing" Her|work=Us Weekly|accessdate=2013-05-06|date=2013-05-06|first=Justin|last=Ravitz|archive-date=2013-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510102519/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/chris-brown-confirms-rihanna-breakup-i-cant-focus-on-wife-ing-her-201365|dead-url=no}}</ref>2015年，蕾哈娜与德克薩斯州[[密蘇里城_(德克薩斯州)|密蘇里城]]的一名饶舌歌手[[特拉维斯·斯科特|特拉维斯·斯科特]]开始交往。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/katy-perry-bff-rihanna-put-6350335|title=Rihanna and Travis Scott Are Officially Dating—All the Details on Their Hot New Romance!|work=E! News|access-date=2015-09-13|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919174035/http://www.mirror.co.uk/3am/celebrity-news/katy-perry-bff-rihanna-put-6350335|dead-url=no}}</ref>2017年至今，她的男友是[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]商人[[哈桑·賈米爾|哈桑·賈米爾]]，這對情侶於2020年1月分手。

2021年5月，[[ASAP_Rocky|A$AP Rocky]]首次公開了他與蕾哈娜的伴侶關係。<ref>{{Cite web|title=A$AP Rocky Opens Up About His Relationship With Rihanna, ‘The Love Of My Life,’ For The First Time|url=https://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a36474120/asap-rocky-rihanna-relationship-interview/|date=2021-05-19|work=ELLE}}</ref>

蕾哈娜是一名基督徒。她在闲暇时光会阅读《[[圣经|圣经]]》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.christianpost.com/news/rihanna-focuses-on-obeying-god-sharing-scripture-with-fans-80115/ |title=Rihanna Focuses on Obeying God, Sharing Scripture With Fans |work=The Christian Post |date=2012-08-16 |accessdate=2014-07-31 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714140955/http://www.christianpost.com/news/rihanna-focuses-on-obeying-god-sharing-scripture-with-fans-80115/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2015年，蕾哈娜曾在《[[时尚芭莎|时尚芭莎]]》的采访中表示，她对上帝的信仰帮助她度过了整个职业生涯。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pulse.com.gh/religion/rihanna-pop-singer-talks-about-her-undying-faith-in-god-id3756646.html|title=Pop singer talks about her undying faith in God|author=Sena Quashie|date=2015|accessdate=2014-11-29|archive-date=2015-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716205555/http://pulse.com.gh/religion/rihanna-pop-singer-talks-about-her-undying-faith-in-god-id3756646.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>她也自称是[[新教|新教]][[靈恩派|靈恩派]]使者[[喬伊斯·邁耶|喬伊斯·邁耶]]的追随者。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.christianpost.com/news/rihanna-shares-joyce-meyers-teachings-with-fans-calls-christian-speaker-awesome-76609/ |title=Rihanna Shares Joyce Meyer's Teachings With Fans, Calls Christian Speaker 'Awesome' |work=The Christian Post |date=2012-06-13 |accessdate=2014-07-31 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714152434/http://www.christianpost.com/news/rihanna-shares-joyce-meyers-teachings-with-fans-calls-christian-speaker-awesome-76609/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

在NCAA三月狂热音乐节中，蕾哈娜表示自己反对《[[恢复宗教自由法_(印第安纳州)|恢复宗教自由法]]》以宗教信仰为由放任个人或企业[[异性恋主义|对LGBT群体的歧视]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/04/06/rihanna-indiana-gay-law_n_7011358.html|title=Rihanna Gets Explicit Telling Indiana Crowd How She Really Feels About Anti-LGBT Law|author=Cavan Sieczkowski|date=2015|accessdate=2014-11-29|archive-date=2015-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409014535/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/04/06/rihanna-indiana-gay-law_n_7011358.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>蕾哈娜还曾与一些名人录制了一段线上影片《如果你是非裔美国人，你的23种遇害方式》（{{lang|en|''23 Ways You Could Be Killed If You Are Black in America''}}）。該影片與我們在這裡行動（{{lang|en|We Are Here Movement}}）合作，呼籲社会採取行動遏制警察当局的暴行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/beyonce-rihanna-more-stars-team-up-for-intense-23-ways-psa-w213011|title=Beyonce, Rihanna: ‘23 Ways You Could Be Killed If You Are Black’|publisher=|accessdate=2017-02-09|archive-date=2016-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161216031718/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/beyonce-rihanna-more-stars-team-up-for-intense-23-ways-psa-w213011|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，Rihanna在Coachella音樂節中配帶一支名為flask bracelet 的首飾引起討論，該手鐲可以隨時倒出預先倒在里面的酒作飲用<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mings-fashion.com/4225-2/ |title=如何在Coachella內隨時有酒飲？有請Rihanna示範手鈪藏酒！ |accessdate=2018-09-01 |archive-date=2018-09-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902060822/https://www.mings-fashion.com/4225-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年，蕾哈娜在[[富比士|富比士]]美國白手起家女富豪榜，以6億美元身價首度入榜，名列第33名。其收入來源，主要是和路威酩軒合作的Fenty Beauty化妝品受歡迎，該產品在2019年銷售額超過6億美元。此外她還與{{link-en|Techstyle Fashion Company|TechStyle Fashion Group}}共同擁有Savage x Fenty的系列內衣，這個內衣品牌2019年總共募集投資5,000萬美元<ref >{{Cite news |url = http://www.forbeschina.com/billionaires/51786 | title = 福布斯發布2020 美國白手起家女富豪榜，總財富額達900億美元 | accessdate=2020-10-30 |agency=Forbes福布斯|date=2020-10-14 }}</ref>。

